snippet.title: TREPANG2 Announcement Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2021
snippet.description: Trepang 2 is an upcoming gun-fu shooter from Trepang Studios and published by Team 17. Watch out for Trepang 2's crunchy gunplay and realistic visuals when it comes to PC in 2022.
